title: 2023 Chevy Corvette C8 Z06: Here's a Thorough Tour of this Beast!
author: Doug DeMuro
description:
CHECK OUT CARS & BIDS!

2023 C8 Corvette Z06 tour! The new 2023 Chevy Corvette Z06 is an impressive car, and it's loaded with upgrades over the regular C8 Corvette. Today I'm taking you on a thorough tour of the C8 Z06, and I'm going to show you some of the quirks and features of the Z06 -- and some of the upgrades over the regular Corvette.
